- `pytest tests/test_vector_engine.py`: Verify PCA denoising, extraction, and projection.
- `pytest tests/test_modules.py`: Test steering logic, norm-relative scaling, tripwires, and bounding boxes.

### Manual Verification
- We will execute `run_pipeline.py` and inspect the console logs to verify that the Aegis firewall intercepts prompts, steers emotions, trips on deceptive inputs, regulates arousal, and enforces the Goldilocks zone under safety evaluations.
